## 5. Security Model

```
Role              Can Access
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SUPER_ADMIN       Everything
CONTENT_ADMIN     Curriculum read/write, Assessment questions
SCHOOL_ADMIN      Students in their own school (read/write)
PSYCHOLOGIST      Assessment responses, Student profiles (read)
STUDENT           Own profile, Questionnaire submit, Curriculum read
```

### JWT Strategy
- Access token: 1 hour expiry
- Refresh token: 7 days
- Stored in HTTP-only cookie OR Authorization header (align with frontend choice)

